Per the Bluetooth BAP specification, BIS_index values are numbered uniquely across the entire BIG (Broadcast Isochronous Group), not per subgroup. The example from the spec shows Subgroup[0] using BIS_index 0x01, 0x02 and Subgroup[1] using 0x03, 0x04 — indices continue sequentially, not restart.

